 * 
 * 比较 $S_i S_j$ 和 $S_j S_i$：
 * 长度 $L_i = n_{1,i} + n_{0,i}$, $L_j = n_{1,j} + n_{0,j}$.
 * 
 * 比较 $S_i S_j$ 和 $S_j S_i$ 等价于比较：
 * $(\text{Value}(S_i) \cdot 2^{L_j} + \text{Value}(S_j))$ vs $(\text{Value}(S_j) \cdot 2^{L_i} + \text{Value}(S_i))$
 * 
 * $\text{Value}(S_i) = \sum_{k=1}^{n_{1,i}} 2^{n_{0,i} + n_{1,i}-k} = (2^{n_{1,i}} - 1) \cdot 2^{n_{0,i}}$ (如果 $n_{1,i}>0$)
 * 
